name: voyage dans l'au-delà
description:
Art developed from studies related to abstract art having influence on artists such as: clyfford still, pierre soulages, jason martin, kazuaki tanahashi and fabienne verdie. My arts are the result of unique feelings, whether the cause is a song, a digital art, a photo, a video of an artist showing his technique, etc...
You can check out more on my twitter: dobbelgarten_
